en_864039_0	The lawsuit pertaining to shooting and killing three persons and injuring another group during a demonstration that was staged demanding drinking water at Rathupaswala in Weliveriya, was summoned in the Gampaha Magistrate’s Court today.
en_864039_1	An attack was unleashed on the people of Rathupaswala who staged a protest in August 2013.
en_864039_2	Three persons were killed in this ordeal while several others sustained injuries.
en_864039_3	Four persons including Brig. DeshapriyaGunawardena have been indicted in relation to this incident.
en_864039_4	They appeared in the Gampaha Magistrate’s Court today.
en_864039_5	The Court ordered that the case be summoned again on April 05th as instructions of the Attorney General had not been received.
